      "content": "# Mini AI Project

This is a simple character-level Markov chain generator implemented in Python without any external dependencies.

## Usage

### Training the Model
```bash
python -m mini_ai.cli train --input <input_text_file> --model-out <output_model_file> --order <order>
```

### Generating Text
```bash
python -m mini_ai.cli generate --model <model_file> --length <text_length> --seed <optional_seed> --random-seed <optional_random_seed>
```
